headline: Is Now the Right Moment for Amex After Its 230% Five-Year Rally?
summary: If you’re holding American Express stock or thinking of jumping in, you’re in line with a lot of investors watching this blue-chip closely. Maybe it’s the company’s strong brand, or the way it always seems to stay ahead when the economy is resilient. In the past five years alone, American Express shares have surged by more than 230.5%, and over the last year, they’re up a steady 21.2%. Even zooming into the last three years, the total return is a striking 137.9%. The jump may seem incredible,...
